titled self-importance.<br /><b><a href="SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Levitate"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Levitate</b><sup>Y</sup><b></a></b>: Subject moves up and down at your direction.<br /><b><a href="SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Life Pact"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Life Pact</a></b>: Affected creatures automatically donate hp to stabilize fallen ally.<br /><b><a href="SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Mind Over Matter"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Mind Over Matter</a></b>: Reassign ability damage/drain from one ability to another.<br /><b><a href="SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Mindshock"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Mindshock</a></b>: Charge your attacks with violent psychic energy.<br /><b><a href="SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Misdirection"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Misdirection</a></b>: Misleads divinations for one creature or object.<br /><b><a href="SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Necrostasis"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Necrostasis</a></b>: Stagger an undead creature<br /><b><a href="SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Object Reading"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Object Reading</a></b>: Read psychic impressions left on an object.<br /><b><a href="SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Phantom Trap"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Phantom Trap</b><sup>M</sup><b></a></b>: Makes item seem trapped.<br /><b><a href="SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Pilfering Hand"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Pilferin